<plot>The series Simonne and Chartrand tells the true story of a couple who marked the Quebec society by disputing it, in the name of an ideal of justice. The life of the two militants and their children who become adult, revives to us the social upheavals which marked the history of Quebec during three decades.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?100588</url></doc>
